Members of the Company pride themselves as Cadets who provide a critical need for the Corps in the performance of music for parades  ceremonies and sporting events at the Institute  All trips outside VMI are funded by the Institute and instruments are provided to the cadets by the school  Selection for participation is through interview and audition  Salute to America s Finest  Songs of the US Armed Forces     Regimental Band  About the Band  VMI Pipe Band  Glee Club  Band Scholarships  Music Selections  Staff Col  John Brodie Director of Music P   540  464 7646 Maj  Burt Mitchell Pipe Band Director P   540  464 7231 Glee Club Director P   540  464 7646 208 Shell Hall Virginia Military Institute Lexington  VA  24450 F   540  464 7209 Regimental Band Regimental Band Regimental Band      Regimental Band Band Company is one of nine companies which make up the Corps of Cadets  Rank structure  academic major  class structure  and athletic structure is identical to the rest of the Corps at large and any cadet is welcome to participate in the Band  Band Company cadets participate in NCAA sports  intramurals  and Rat Training  as well as guard and company functions  Members of the Company pride themselves as Cadets who provide a critical need for the Corps in the performance of music for parades  ceremonies and sporting events at the Institute  All trips outside VMI are funded by the Institute and instruments are provided to the cadets by the school  Selection for participation is through interview and audition  Salute to America s Finest  Songs of the US Armed Forces Regimental Band Band Company is one of nine companies which make up the Corps of Cadets  Rank structure  academic major  class structure  and athletic structure is identical to the rest of the Corps at large and any cadet is welcome to participate in the Band  Band Company cadets participate in NCAA sports  intramurals  and Rat Training  as well as guard and company functions  Members of the Company pride them